[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.293,
    "text": "Hi, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.169,
    "endTime": 3.17,
    "text": "Hello?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.253,
    "endTime": 4.963,
    "text": "Patrick, it's me, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.339,
    "endTime": 7.966,
    "text": "Ah! Hold on, buddy. I'll get you out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.719,
    "endTime": 12.677999999999999,
    "text": "SpongeBob? SpongeBob?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.763,
    "endTime": 14.264,
    "text": "- Patrick... - SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.807,
    "endTime": 19.102,
    "text": "- SpongeBob! - Patrick, I'm right behind you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.186,
    "endTime": 20.354,
    "text": "There you are!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.031,
    "endTime": 34.992,
    "text": "This show was filmed in front of a live studio audience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.077,
    "endTime": 36.995,
    "text": "Happy Valentine's Day!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.162,
    "endTime": 40.415,
    "text": "- Here's your present. - And I have a present for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.624,
    "endTime": 43.168,
    "text": "- You do? - It's the greatest..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.044,
    "endTime": 45.379,
    "text": "The bestest..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.171,
    "endTime": 48.006,
    "text": "The most fantabulous..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.258,
    "endTime": 52.469,
    "text": "Present ever! But you can't have it yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.095,
    "endTime": 55.18,
    "text": "- Why not? - 'Cause it's not ready yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.264,
    "endTime": 58.35,
    "text": "- Is it ready now? - Do you wanna ruin the surprise?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.392,
    "endTime": 61.353,
    "text": "Yes! You gotta tell me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.645,
    "endTime": 64.897,
    "text": "No can do. You'll just have to wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.065,
    "endTime": 67.568,
    "text": "Please, please, please, please! Tell me! Tell me! Tell me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.818,
    "endTime": 68.986,
    "text": "Please!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.194,
    "endTime": 70.529,
    "text": "OK, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.737,
    "endTime": 72.03,
    "text": "Here we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.115,
    "endTime": 75.741,
    "text": "You got me a carnival?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.118,
    "endTime": 77.869,
    "text": "Mine, mine, mine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.078,
    "endTime": 80.289,
    "text": "Alright, everybody out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.455,
    "endTime": 83.834,
    "text": "- This is my carnival! - It's not the carnival."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.917,
    "endTime": 85.08500000000001,
    "text": "- Oh... - Here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.169,
    "endTime": 88.589,
    "text": "- Why don't you take this quarter and-- - Oh my gosh, a quarter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.672,
    "endTime": 91.383,
    "text": "- I've always wanted a quarter! - It's not the quarter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.466,
    "endTime": 92.467,
    "text": "Oh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.968,
    "endTime": 97.63900000000001,
    "text": "I'm ready for the greatest Valentine's present in the whole world now, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.723,
    "endTime": 99.6,
    "text": "Well, this is where you're gonna get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.976,
    "endTime": 102.102,
    "text": "I hope..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.311,
    "endTime": 104.146,
    "text": "Just keep looking out there, pal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.523,
    "endTime": 110.569,
    "text": "Patrick, you know how sometimes you plan something special,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.611,
    "endTime": 112.946,
    "text": "- and things just don't work out? - No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.866,
    "endTime": 119.036,
    "text": "Holy Mackerel, is it hot up here or what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.457,
    "endTime": 125.333,
    "text": "Patrick! Here it is!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.044,
    "endTime": 129.04500000000002,
    "text": "What's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.128,
    "endTime": 131.21499999999997,
    "text": "A handshake, a friendly handshake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.548,
    "endTime": 132.966,
    "text": "A handshake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.342,
    "endTime": 134.67600000000002,
    "text": "That's the big gift?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.01,
    "endTime": 136.97,
    "text": "You got me a handshake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.054,
    "endTime": 138.972,
    "text": "Happy Valentine's Day!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.333,
    "endTime": 167.584,
    "text": "I've been thinking..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.126,
    "endTime": 171.421,
    "text": "At first a handshake doesn't seem like much but,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.839,
    "endTime": 174.424,
    "text": "- really it's the thought that counts. - Hey, SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.508,
    "endTime": 177.05200000000002,
    "text": "I just wanted to thank you for this box of chocolates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.177,
    "endTime": 178.262,
    "text": "No problem, Fran."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.303,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "I mean, even though I was expecting more..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.014,
    "endTime": 184.101,
    "text": "Thanks for the roses, SpongeBob. Happy Valentine's Day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.184,
    "endTime": 185.477,
    "text": "You too, Dave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.602,
    "endTime": 188.35500000000002,
    "text": "And not that it matters that we've been friends for so long..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.397,
    "endTime": 190.315,
    "text": "Hey SpongeBob, thanks for the bike."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.399,
    "endTime": 192.901,
    "text": "Can you believe this guy? I just met him this morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.194,
    "endTime": 196.321,
    "text": "So, as I was saying..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.363,
    "endTime": 198.198,
    "text": "Excuse me. Do you guys have the time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.24,
    "endTime": 202.035,
    "text": "Ah! Patrick needs love too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.79,
    "endTime": 209.626,
    "text": "I defy you, heart man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.628,
    "endTime": 215.339,
    "text": "Attention everyone, there's a chubby pink starfish on the loose."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.098,
    "endTime": 226.894,
    "text": "Give me SpongeBob!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.104,
    "endTime": 230.77200000000002,
    "text": "You broke my heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.981,
    "endTime": 233.942,
    "text": "Now I'm gonna break something of yours!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.026,
    "endTime": 238.197,
    "text": "OK Patrick, I know I deserve this, but do they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.739,
    "endTime": 241.241,
    "text": "They didn't give me anything either."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.534,
    "endTime": 244.87,
    "text": "Nope, it's too late for that now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.37,
    "endTime": 247.08,
    "text": "For all of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.168,
    "endTime": 254.796,
    "text": "Yeehaw! Get along, little shellfish!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.255,
    "endTime": 256.964,
    "text": "Gallop, you scallops!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.216,
    "endTime": 258.926,
    "text": "Yeah, Sandy's here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.009,
    "endTime": 261.553,
    "text": "Woo! Look Patrick, it's here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.891,
    "endTime": 268.93600000000004,
    "text": "- Happy Valentine's Day, Patrick! - Yay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.436,
    "endTime": 270.77,
    "text": "Yay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.271,
    "endTime": 273.857,
    "text": "My valentine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.358,
    "endTime": 276.693,
    "text": "Hey, is this solid chocolate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.777,
    "endTime": 278.07,
    "text": "Patrick, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.907,
    "endTime": 286.578,
    "text": "oh SpongeBob, you didn't have to get me anything."
  }
]